skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cranky robot
des:
Sometimes Alexa doesn't feel like answering your questions! Ask Cranky Robot anything and get a cranky reply.

This is a simple novelty skill where Alexa will give you a snarky reply instead of answering your question. You can ask Cranky Robot any kind of question and totally not get the answer you're looking for.

Guidance suggested.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
